{"word":"H7597 - שְׁאַלְתִּיאֵל - Shᵉʼaltîyʼêl - sheh-al-tee-ale' - Shalthiel","slug":"H7597","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שְׁאַלְתִּיאֵל</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Shᵉʼaltîyʼêl"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>sheh-al-tee-ale'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Shalthiel"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>שׁלתּיאל שׁאלתּיאל</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>she'altı̂y'êl shaltı̂y'êl</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>sheh-al-tee-ale'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Shealtiel or Salathiel = \"I have asked of God\" <ol><li>father of Zerubbabel</li><li>son of king Jehoiachin or Jeconiah or Coniah of Judah and uncle of Zerubbabel</li></ol> <p />Origin: from <a href=\"#/H7592\">H7592</a> and <a href=\"#/H410\">H410</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Masculine "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7969\">H7969</a>, <a href=\"#/H7970\">H7970</a>, <a href=\"#/H7991\">H7991</a>, <a href=\"#/H7992\">H7992</a>, <a href=\"#/H8027\">H8027</a>, <a href=\"#/H8028\">H8028</a>, <a href=\"#/H8029\">H8029</a>, <a href=\"#/H8030\">H8030</a>, <a href=\"#/H8031\">H8031</a>, <a href=\"#/H8032\">H8032</a>"}]}